    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Procedural Whodunit Murder Mystery Detective Cruise Vacation Simulator</strong></h2>It is 1982 and you are the world's most famous detective - and taking a well-deserved vacation on your favorite cruise ship - The Stella. But there's a murder. <i>Again</i>.<br><br><strong>Murder on the Stella</strong> is a murder mystery adventure cruise ship vacation simulator. Wait, is this even a genre? Anyway, it's different each time you play - different cases, different suspects, different weapons, different motives. And different destinations.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Investigate!</strong></h2>Inspect the ship, search for clues and weapons, interrogate suspects - and solve the case before the ship reaches its destination.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Convict!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/f3fcd39d28b93b6805578460e5a65cbc.poster.avif?t=1768508079\" width=616 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/f3fcd39d28b93b6805578460e5a65cbc.webm?t=1768508079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/f3fcd39d28b93b6805578460e5a65cbc.mp4?t=1768508079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In classical murder mystery fashion... you know everything about the killer, the weapon and the motive? Then gather the passengers and crew in the ship's lobby and solve the murder.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Relax!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/3209bdd1958dfc89728f485b11789042.poster.avif?t=1768508079\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/3209bdd1958dfc89728f485b11789042.webm?t=1768508079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/3209bdd1958dfc89728f485b11789042.mp4?t=1768508079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Enjoy the life aboard the ship - it's your vacation isn't it? Play arcade games, go to the gym, take a swim in the pool, get a drink at the bar. And maybe there's a clue as well.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Travel!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/21675c2794560667e0d17dbf30b8e98d.poster.avif?t=1768508079\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/21675c2794560667e0d17dbf30b8e98d.webm?t=1768508079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/21675c2794560667e0d17dbf30b8e98d.mp4?t=1768508079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/5cf71472fca06c2a3f754e88eaf8d7c1.poster.avif?t=1768508079\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/5cf71472fca06c2a3f754e88eaf8d7c1.webm?t=1768508079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156890/extras/5cf71472fca06c2a3f754e88eaf8d7c1.mp4?t=1768508079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Different destinations make each cruise a unique experience - marvel at the pyramids of Egypt or savor a starlit night in the Arctic Ocean.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Graphics like it's 1982 - but in 3D and with a one-shot camera!<br></li><li>Kind of roguelite-like, but you can't die!<br></li><li>Day/night cycle!<br></li><li>More than 50 different characters with individual personalities!<br></li><li>A different case each time you play!</li></ul><br><br><strong><i>More details coming soon!</i></strong>",
